  "title": "Student Care Assistant Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist main teacher to plan, supervise, and implement the program for the class in accordance with the policies, guidelines, framework, and philosophy of the centre</li><li>Responsible for all aspects of classroom management and carry out routine care duties to ensure safety and hygiene of the children</li><li>Maintain and build relationships with children and parents.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Skills and Knowledge Required:</strong></p><ul><li>Enjoy working with Children</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to work well independently as well as within a team</li><li>Experience with young children be added advantage</li><li>Able to assist with <u><strong>Mandarin homework</strong></u></li></ul><p></p><p>Candidate who is keen in building a solid teaching career and be a part of the ‘kampung spirit’ team is warmly welcome to send an updated resume to <em>hr.dncedu@gmail.com</em></p>",
